dct_title_s: Map Accompanying Report of Chief Engineer on Proposed Bayhead-Manasquan Canal
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Barnegat Inlet to Manasquan River along the Atlantic Ocean and including Barnegat Bay. Map depicts the proposed canal to be dredged from the Metedeconk River to the Manasquan River.
